<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="make-fun-of">make fun of</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>取笑；拿…开玩笑：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don't feel sorry for the disabled or make fun of them, and don't ignore them either.
不要感到残疾人可怜，或者取笑他们，也别不理睬他们。</p><footer>人教⑦ – 1</footer></div></div>